ms inside a stadium.The IOC said athletes from Russia and Belarus who are approved to compete at the Olympics as neutrals will have a chance only \\\"to experience the event\\\" - likely watching from near the river.\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 1031, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 412, \"end\": 419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Florian\", \"score\": 0.9409751771390915, \"rank\": 0.06272725352155174, \"text\": \"Florian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Florian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Florian\"}, {\"begin\": 429, \"end\": 439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.064957746266494e-14, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 458, \"end\": 469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.9998110317571464, \"rank\": 0.00018717091547055254, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}, {\"begin\": 471, \"end\": 478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.5652350468143658, \"rank\": 0.7673096634142546, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 483, \"end\": 493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\", \"score\": 0.9999880644750802, \"rank\": 1.1114390487396387e-05, \"text\": \"Belarusian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\"}, {\"begin\": 613, \"end\": 616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"